songs.lyrics:
Hook:
(Cuban Doll)
Imma gangsta bitch
Imma pistol poppin’ get it out the mud bitch
I’m the type of bitch you might just fall in love with
Yeah I’m looking for the money, where the plug at?
(Asian Doll)
Imma rich bitch
Finesse a nigga out his life, he ain’t get shit
All my bundles come free, imma lit bitch
Think that bitch mad she ain’t his bitch
Aye! Aye!

Verse 1: (Cuban Doll)
I don’t gotta use no chop, I’ll drop shit
I ain’t flexin for the gram, bitch fuck a pic
All my bitches getting money, we ain’t doing dicks
And your nigga taking orders, he a fucking trick

Verse 2: (Asian Doll)
I ain’t flexin’ for no nigga who ain’t got shit
I ain’t tweetin’ bout no bitch, imma spot them
All my niggas really killers, get mopped quick
Bitch you broke, and you mad Imma hot bitch

Verse 3: (Honey Oso)
Uh!
I don’t gotta talk big, bitch I’m bout it bout it
Pop up at yo crib, make you come up out it
I’ll take a bitch nigga, have her in her body
Name honey bitch, you can come and lick it off me

Verse 5: (Cuban Doll)
Big mouth, lil hair, lil bitch retarded
Putting on a show, leave her on the red carpet
Before we up them chops, on you weak bitches
We’ll pull up to your crib, and just beat bitches

Verse 6: (Asian Doll)
All that Instagram flexin, get yo weave snatched
Smack her in the mouth, don’t wanna hear no feedback
Niggas got you on a leash, you a bad puppy
Bitch you better keep a buzz off that rap money
